    "Evaluate how CESM can have the potential to enhance the diagnostic accuracy comparing to Digital Mammography (DM). 4.",
    "Assess the performance of YOLOv4, YOLOv7, and YOLOv8 in mass detection on CDD-CESM and INbreast dataset based on a comprehensive evaluation through different experiments. 5.",
